{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be rustic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Fortress Security</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/brushed-alum.png'); /* Rustic texture */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #a52a2a; /* Rustic red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #6b1a1a 5px solid; /* Darker red border */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        h2, h3 {\n            color: #a52a2a;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #c0c0c0;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #fafafa;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n        footer {\n        