v>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Data Encryption</h3>\n                    <p>Implementing advanced encryption protocols to protect sensitive information.</p>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section id=\"contact\">\n                <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n                <p>Ready to strengthen your defenses? Contact us today for a free consultation.</p>\n                <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea placeholder=\"Message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </section>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Fortress Security. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}